  "Description": {
    "English": "A synthetic lubricant that reduces wear and prolongs the lifespan of technologies with moving parts.<br><br>Crafted from <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Faecium</span> and <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Gamma Root</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种合成润滑剂，能够减少磨损并延长移动零件的技术寿命。<br><br>由<span class=\"name name-fuel\">屎球菌</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">伽马根</span>制作而成。",
    "TencentChinese": "一种合成润滑剂，能够减少磨损并延长移动零件的技术寿命。<br><br>由<span class=\"name name-fuel\">屎球菌</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">伽马根</span>制作而成。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "合成潤滑劑，能減少磨損，延長有可動零件的科技之使用壽命。<br><br>可使用<span class=\"name name-fuel\">屎菌</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">伽瑪根</span>製造。"
  },
