  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "Craft from <span class=\"name name-fuel\">Faecium</span> and <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Gamma Root</span>. Learn the blueprint with the aid of a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Science Specialist</span> in a base.<br>Gamma Root can be farmed, or found wild on <span class=\"name name-commodity\">radioactive planets</span>.<br>Faecium is harvested from the excrement of wild animals. Feed wild animals to increase production.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "由<span class=\"name name-fuel\">屎球菌</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">伽马根</span>制作而成。在基地中，在<span class=\"name name-technology\">科学专家</span>的帮助下学习设计图。<br>伽马根可以通过种植获得，也能在<span class=\"name name-commodity\">辐射星球</span>的野外找到。<br>屎球菌能从野生动物排泄物中采集到。喂养野生动物来提升产量。",
    "TencentChinese": "由<span class=\"name name-fuel\">屎球菌</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">伽马根</span>制作而成。在基地中，在<span class=\"name name-technology\">科学专家</span>的帮助下学习设计图。<br>伽马根可以通过种植获得，也能在<span class=\"name name-commodity\">辐射星球</span>的野外找到。<br>屎球菌能从野生动物排泄物中采集到。喂养野生动物来提升产量。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "以<span class=\"name name-fuel\">屎菌</span>和<span class=\"name name-tradeable\">伽瑪根</span>製造。在基地中可尋求<span class=\"name name-technology\">科學專家</span>協助，學習設計圖。<br>伽瑪根可栽種，亦可在<span class=\"name name-commodity\">輻射星球</span>野外採集。<br>屎菌則可從野生動物排遺物中採收，餵食野生動物可增加產量。"
  },
